high_descs: Turn right and walk around the dining table to the other side
Grab the plate by the remote
Turn right and walk around the dining table to the floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Grab the plate on the dining table, turn on the floor lamp

high_descs: Turn to your right and go toward the green rug, then turn right and go toward the metal wastebasket. At the wastebasket, turn right and go between the white chairs to the edge of the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn to your right and go back toward the wastebasket, then turn left to go between the table on your left and the green rug on your right, moving forward until you come to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a plate in the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk around the large white table to where the plate is next to a remote and a set of keys.
Pick up the plate off of the table.
Turn around and take a step, then turn left and walk over to the tall lamp in between the door and the couch.
Turn on the light of the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a plate in the light of a tall lamp.
